      <title>希腊银行业在痛苦转型后寻求海外交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/greek-banks-looking-at-deals-abroad-after-painful-restructurings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[希腊最大银行的高管表示，经过多年痛苦的重组后，希腊银行已准备好在海外投资。]]></description>
